name: ULTIMATE INTERSTELLAR CAT INVASION
description:
"ULTIMATE INTERSTELLAR CAT INVASION"

Made by Pius Olver, August 7, 2021, using Unity

Shoot the flying cats to get the high score!

Controls

Fly Up and Down with "W" and "S" or with the "ARROW KEYS"

Shoot lasers with "Left Mouse Button" or "SPACE BAR"

Music was from Gustav Holst's "The Planets: Jupiter Theme" performed by Pius Olver.

Graphic Art was taken from online.
